{
  "stem": "18068.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'll tell him to keep the two boys together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's all you know about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's all we know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We weren't allowed to have cameras.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because in case we were captured, and the Germans-- well, knew exactly where we were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We weren't allowed to keep-- keep a diary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I saw the German women digging graves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's all I saw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I walked into one of the camps, it was a hutted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was three banks, and they were lying the inmates-- I'm sorry I use that term-- they were lying all on top of each other.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just in a filthy state, and they had typhus.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And their bowels were working and running.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what did they do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't get off the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wherever they were, they used it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was all over the floor, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And were there rabbis there, to-- to perform--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the graves weren't marked in any way--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All we saw was digging the graves, [BACKGROUND NOISE] but that's about all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See, we were in a field unit, with no facilities for anything like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Americans were a bit more down south.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were north.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Going towards Hamburg, and so on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The women, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What we had to do, as they washed each one down, all they were-- the inmates-- skin and bone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You saw their chest, like a bird cage covered with skin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They [INAUDIBLE] thin.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to demonstrate to the German women, see, this man is a normal man-- he was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Look at him now, a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Thank Hitler for this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And how did they respond to that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, most of them say they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Could be true, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
